                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><strong>Suitability</strong></td>
                  <td>‚ùå Many contraindications</td>
                  <td>‚úÖ Suitable for most people</td>
                  <td>‚ö†Ô∏è Limited to accessible wax</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><strong>Cost</strong></td>
                  <td>‚úÖ Most affordable</td>
                  <td>‚ö†Ô∏è Higher cost</td>
                  <td>‚úÖ Moderate cost</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
