                  <td>‚ö†Ô∏è Can be uncomfortable</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><strong>Time Required</strong></td>
                  <td>‚ö†Ô∏è 20-40 minutes</td>
                  <td>‚úÖ 15-25 minutes</td>
                  <td>‚úÖ 10-20 minutes</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
